Wow I have been so busy but I do have something I want to post...It's from my MySpace....To my close friends who I luv very much.

Sarah Beavis-thanks for being such a good friend through all the bullshit. For the last five years, you have stuck beside me. You are one day younger than me, but that doesn't change anything. I trust you with everything. I know I can go to you for everything. I mean in our five years of our friendship, we only got into one fight. But that fight only bought us closer. You are truly and honestly my first best friend. I love you like a sister. You are an aunt to my kids when I have them. You are hopefully going to be my room mate after high school. You are going to be my maid of honor at my wedding. That's how much you mean to me. We have been through so much together in five years. But I can say this. We really have not been best friends. Because through it all we have been BEST FRIENDS! WE HATE THE BITCH...lol!

Emily Bridgers-Emi, thanks for being such a good friend to me in the year and a half of our friendship. We have had so many ups and downs, but here we are. You are my second best friend. Thanks for being such a great person and friend. Thank you for being the person I went to for everything. Thank you for never betraying me. You were always a good friend to me and you never proved me wrong. You were always trustworthy and I knew that. I knew you would never let me down. Thank you for being my second best friend.

Chris Rochelle-you have been such a good friend to me in the last year. I know we've known each other for a long time and I know we used to not like each other, but thanks for this year. You have been such a good friend to me. You have helped me through so much and I don't know what I would do everything. You have never left my side. You have been such a good shoulder to cry on. Thanks for always sticking beside me and I do know you are a true friend. Chris, you have always found a way to make me feel okay. You always found a way to cheer me up. When I was low, I knew I could go to you. Even when i was a bitch, you never left my side. Through it the drama and lies I got told, you were there. Through all the fights, I still had your friendship. I always found it hard to believe how much of a good friend you were because you always found a way to outstand me more. You prove how much more of a good friend you were. On homecoming night, at the game, when I started to cry (ONLY you know why), you just grabbed me and held me and told me everything was going to be okay. And it was. Thanks to you. You were there for me on Brandon's birthday which was a hard day for me. You knew how much I loved Brandon and how much he meant ot me, so you were there for me. You stood beside me. I LOVE YOU LIKE A BROTHER!

Zach Hahn-you have a big heart and I'm so happy that I met you this year. You have been such a great friend to me. I thank you for always being there for me. I do love you and thank you. You have been such a good friend to me. KEEP BEING A GREAT FRIEND AND PERSON. You have been there for me through so much drama and bullshit. Through all the lies people told me. The whole time telling me it's okay. You have been such a good influence on me...meaning you made me learn to trust again. You made me learn it's okay to be who I am. To open up and show people my true colors. To not keep the people who isn't true to me in my life. You opened up my eyes to who I can be. To be daring, to be courageous, TO NOT BE SCARED! You  knew I needed that, so you gave me it. You made me feel worth something. You are one my best friends. You were there for me through all my tears over Brandon...which was ALOT!

Gina Abraham-we have been through so much no names, but we both know who). Here we are.....you being one of my best friends. You are someone I know I can go to when I need a shoulder to lean on. And someone I know will be there for me. You helped me through all the KC drama. You were the first to know about "Jose" and "Tom." You never told anyone about those crushes and I still haven't told anyone about "Joe" and I'm not planning on it. Yeah I know KB caused alot of shit between us, but we got through it. We might not have known each other long. But just know that I love you. You never judged me...even when I thought I deserved it.You always stuck beside me and I do thank you for that. Even when KB tried to end our friendship, we didn't except for once (and we discussed it). I'm so happy we made it this far and our frienship is only growing stronger. I hope you know I never wanted to try to seem like I was trying ot end your relationship woth Kyle. I just didn't want you to get hurt. I didn't want your heart to get broken. I LOVE YOU!Through everything you were there for me. You never left my me and you never betrayed me. Kyle might have put us both in tight spots in our friendship but we looked past it. I know you love Kyle and I don't want to stand between that. I don't want you to think I HATE him. I just DISLIKE him. I just want you to be happy and not hurting. I just don't want you to regret anything. You know you are one of my best friends.

Brittany Spencer-Brit, we have been friends since seventh grde and we have been in almost six fights. but we still are friends. You are one of my best friends. Thank you for being there for me through so much. It's just so funny how our friendship went down in four years. But I knew you were a good friend. You are a great person. I don't care if my mom really doesn't like you. I do 

Nathan Garrison-Nate, wow I only met you this year, but I got so close to you. Thank you for being there for me and being such a great friend to me. I'm so grateful that I met you and that we became friends. Thank you so much for being there for me when I need you. I LOVE YOU SO MUCH FROM THE BOTTOM OF MY HEART! You and I have been through so much, but yet you were always there for me. You were always true to me. You were kind and caring towards me. You were there for me when I was crying. You even said you would beat up anyone who made me cry. You even once said that I was to sweet to be upset.You don't understand how much that meant to me. I LOVE YOU! You told me things that I didn't believe, but I now do. You told me I was sweet, caring and a good friend. When you tears in my eyes, you always offered a shoulder.

Lucas Harrison-you have been such a great friend to me in the last year. I may have met you this year, but you have become one of my best friends. You have been there for me through so much drama. You were always so caring, and very nice to me. The only reason our friendship started was because your brother Everett was one of my best friends (still is). You were there for me through all the tears and bitchy moments. You are really one of my best friends.

Everyone says that he won't hurt me but I just don't know what to believe because Kayce said the same thing and so did everyone else, but look what happened there. Also by the way Kayce....I think....wants to talk to me again, but I just don't want to try that again. I just don't want to get hurt again. I can't stand that. I don't want to be suicidal again. Wow in less than 18 days i am turning 16. i have invited almost everyone i know. yes both of those guys are invited. which sucks. since the new one hates the old one. so yeah...DRAMA!!! i wrote the new one a letter which i am going to type right now...

well since we are friends, i think u need to know some things. when i was barely two my real dad walked out on me. i never heard from him until i went to foster care in 7th grade. i went to foster care because my step-dad abused me-physically. i would be scared when someone would even touch me-poke me, anything. i woulld explode into tears. i think that's why i'm so affectionate. but back to the point, i had to stay there for three months-thanksgiving, christmas, new years' eve and new year's day to. i was only 12 ( going on 13) years old. then in 8th grade i met this girl who kinda ruined my life. she started to start drama and ruin friendships. she started to say lies to my face-saying we were friends but saying to others "god i ahte her." i heard that she would call me 'ugly', 'bitchy', 'fat', and so much more. it hurt me. it would kill me inside. i thought she was my best friend. then in 9th grade, i hung out with this girl (a diiferent one) who got me into some trouble. she would push me into skipping and fighting. then in may 2006 on the 31st-almost two weeks after i turned 15-this guy i grew up with, stephen plocki, died. he was like my brother. i known him my entire life and it didn't go down well. he died at the age of 20. if he was still here he would be 21-his birthday was april 4th. then august 16 in the same year, my best friend, brandon herriott, died. he was only 17. if he lived for two more months he would have turned 18. but two weeks before he died, i met this guy named kayce maultsby on myspace. he was the person i went to when brandon died. brandon was the first gut i trusted and i cared about. he was the first guy who cared about me, really cared. kayce was there when i nedded someone. also during the time, i was with this guy who wasn't the best boyfriend ever. he kinda hurt me and put me throuugh so much of our one month of dating. then around october 19th-brandon's brithday-i started to get depressed. BADLY!! then i started to fall for kayce hard. so i started to write him this note telling him how i felt. but my feelings got so much stronger i had to re-write the letter. i thought he was a good influence on me, but he got me into drinking and partying. i started to act slutty. i did somethings with him i now regret. he has been down my pants and has touched my boobs skin-on-skin. i have been down his pants. we have kissed. let's just say the list goes on. we were sexual. then in january of this year, i re-wrote the letter. i told him i loved him and i wanted to be with him. he broke my heart. for three weeks-whole three weeks-i was suicidal and depressed. i tried to committ suicide twice or at least four times. all because of him. but i tried to convince myself he was worth it. then he waits a while to tell me he has a fucking girlfriend. i thought i wasn't worth no one's time. i know i am-i got friends who love and support me through everything. but he kept on playing with my heart he would ask for my forgiveness, so i would always forgive. but he would just hurt me AGAIN!! it just kept going on and on for four whole months. then his girlfriend sent me a message on myspace under his profile a month ago threatening me, saying that i should stay away from him because she thought of me as competition! i was like so upset. i went to school and almost cried everytime i saw him. everytime u would see me cry was because of him. he made me feel sop totally worthless. he broke my heart four times in the last four months. i don't want to get hurt again. i don't trust guys at all. because everytime i trust a guy i get my heart broken. that's why i'm so affectionate towards my guy friends. i like to show how much i care about them and that i trust them. and since i trust them, that's unique. so i show it. i do hold hands with them, kiss them and hug them. that's why i'm afraid to open up and i don't want to be in a relationship, only to still be in love with kayce. why do you think i haven't had a boyfriend since i known you? kayce closed my heart up to love, my heart up completely, and to dating.
